2️⃣ Enterprise Example:-
SoD Violation:-
Policy:-
User cannot have Create_Payment + Approve_Payment role

Violation:-
Rahul has both roles

Remediation Options:-
Automatic → Revoke Approve_Payment role
Manual → Send alert to manager for approval
