()Identity Attribute Violation:-
🔥 1. Identity Attribute Violation kya hai?
👉 Jab Identity ke kisi attribute ki value policy/rule ko violate kare,
👉 usko bolte hai Identity Attribute Violation
📌 Example:-
Identity ke attributes:-
email
department
location
manager
employeeType

👉 Ab policy hai:-
❗ “Email mandatory hona chahiye”
👉 Lekin:-
email = null
👉 ❌ Ye violation hai
👉 ✅ Identity Attribute Violation

🔥 4. SailPoint me kaise detect hota hai?

👉 PolicyEvaluator / Identity Refresh ke time

Flow:

Identity Refresh
      ↓
Attribute Check
      ↓
Policy Validation
      ↓
Violation Detect
      ↓
Violation Create
-----------------------------------
🔥 5. Kaun detect karta hai?
👉 PolicyEvaluator
👉 Identity Refresh Task

🔥 6. Violation kaha store hota hai?
👉 ❌ DB me directly attribute nahi
👉 ✅ Lekin violation object store hota hai
👉 Tables / objects:-
Identity
PolicyViolation
ComplianceViolation
----------------------------------------
ex:-
Policy:-
Finance users cannot access HRSystem

Violation:-
John from Finance accessed HRSystem

Remediation Options:-
Automatic → Remove HRSystem access
Manual → Alert security / manager
